#: addon.display_out.DisplayOut:1 d244f3767c9a4839a46690b2aad306a6 of
msgid "Create an HDMI display output for Unit PoE-P4."
msgstr "为 Unit PoE-P4 创建 HDMI 显示输出。"

#: 70f6818cc2de4f0bb5f2886b7d6ebc83 addon.display_out.DisplayOut:3 of
msgid ""
"``DisplayOut`` registers the Unit PoE-P4 HDMI output as an M5 display and"
" returns the display object created by ``M5.addDisplay``. The display can"
" then be used by the standard M5 display APIs."
msgstr ""
"``DisplayOut`` 将 Unit PoE-P4 HDMI 输出注册为显示器，并返回由 ``M5.addDisplay`` "
"创建的显示对象。随后可通过标准显示 API 使用该显示器。"

#: 61dfb6f9ac604243b5095db929fd7f69 addon.display_out.DisplayOut of
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr ""

#: 765e85e0d0064497bc5a5c6f5fc72743 addon.display_out.DisplayOut:7 of
msgid "The logical width of the HDMI output. Default is ``1280``."
msgstr "HDMI 输出的逻辑宽度。默认值为 ``1280``。"

#: 205e860fc7d24410853a3b9227847323 addon.display_out.DisplayOut:8 of
msgid "The logical height of the HDMI output. Default is ``720``."
msgstr "HDMI 输出的逻辑高度。默认值为 ``720``。"

#: 8bd182e0f7b843ff9975420c7a0f4687 addon.display_out.DisplayOut:9 of
msgid "The refresh rate of the HDMI output in Hz. Default is ``60``."
msgstr "HDMI 输出的刷新率，单位为 Hz。默认值为 ``60``。"

#: 0594aacf1d17484a9fcd4bf790d37c8f addon.display_out.DisplayOut of
msgid "Returns"
msgstr ""

#: aacaa57ec39d4d26bbac6e43e65235a0 addon.display_out.DisplayOut:10 of
msgid "The display object registered by ``M5.addDisplay``."
msgstr "由 ``M5.addDisplay`` 注册的显示对象。"

#: 7a47d3d086aa4422b3aa9c9ad2d8d23b addon.display_out.DisplayOut of
msgid "Return type"
msgstr ""

#: 1c899881e36743f3aa806a4e29b66fdc addon.display_out.DisplayOut:15 of
msgid ""
"Unit PoE-P4 HDMI output supports ``1280x720@60Hz`` and ``1920x1080@30Hz``"
" timings."
msgstr "Unit PoE-P4 HDMI 输出支持 ``1280x720@60Hz`` 和 ``1920x1080@30Hz`` 时序。"

